<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Email Confirmation Thank You</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h2 {
            color: #333;
        }
        p {
            color: #666;
        }
        .email-address {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #007bff;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Thank You for Confirming Your Email Address!</h2>
        <p>Your account details have been sent to your email address:</p>
     <p class="email-address"><%= userEmail %></p>
        <p>Please check your inbox for a confirmation email containing your account information.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>